	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=61546><span id=Sage>Slipskin</span></a><br><b><span id=Sage>Sage</span></b><br><span id=notbold>1056 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent [4.75]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>It may be your internet connection or something that changed on your system.&nbsp;&nbsp;i play on an old P 350Mhz box with 256 MB RAM and a cable modem. I can twist 3 songs nearly all the time and sometimes 4.  However, some zones have more lag due to complex graphics than others.  In Paludal Caverns I have trouble twisting more than 2 songs, for example. Try turning off the sky. Do a /showgrass off to turn off little bitty plant movements.  Turn down your clip plane. See if that helps.</p>&nbsp;<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=104222" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=104222</a><br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=479760" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=479760</a></td></td></tr>
