	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=106592><span id= >Colt</span></a><br><span id=notbold>11 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Im thinking about being a bard and i cant get over the fact that they dont have a Double Attack (or at least thats what is says in the books).&nbsp;&nbsp;is it hard to deal damage as a bard without DA? Any help would be GREATLY appreciated... thanks&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>&nbsp;<br>Revenar,<br>Outrider of Tunare</td></td></tr>
