	     <br clear=all><small>Posted @ Wed, Jan 8th 9:35 PM 2003</small></td></tr>
	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=200639><span id= >Ronney</span></a><br><span id=notbold>3 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Just a quick reply to the above post ...<br><br>Note that the original poster said they had 1500pp.&nbsp;&nbsp;Sure, rygorr and velium jewelry is nice (I'd agree with the fire rings 100pc) .... but its not going to make your cash go far at all (in contrast, Jagged Bands AC5 STR3 can be bought for 50pp/pair on AB).  Lambent stats are inferior to VC plate (looks naff too), and is slightly more expensive. Rygorr is really rather good ... but it costs somewhat more than VC on my server, and like lambent the stats are spread out into ares of less benefit at low lvl.  VC would be my armour of choice to quickly level a new char **on a budget**.  <br><br>To compare sets (excl. belt/collar/shoulder/face which are missing in lambent+ry'gorr) :<br><br>VC - 100AC 48STR -22AGI 57HP<br>Lambent - 99AC 10CHA 4STR 5 STA/DEX/AGI/INT (+4 all resists)<br>Ry'gorr - 94AC 19STR 5CHA 2DEX 6STA 45mana 25HP (+low resists)<br><br>It must be remembered that a +48 STR onto a base ATK value of 100 at low lvl is rather more significant than the same modifier to an ATK value of 800 many lvls later.  If there was a bit more than 1500pp I'd mix and match the sets to get the most useful peices from each.<br><br>Re CHA - perhaps I was a little harsh :) But I'd still hold that STR/AC (and HP, *especially* very early on) help a lot more 'til mid levels.<br><br>Re CSS/CLS - good weapons, for sure. But, assuming weapon choice is based upon what will remain best for as many levels as possible, the Crystalline Short Sword has better stats than the CLS (for a bard, at least) and can be bought for half the price (added stats are really only useful to bards, so less well known than the Centis).  Again, to compare :<br><br>CSS  : 12 25 5STR 5STA<br>CLS  : 14 27 8STR 8STA<br>CrSS : 12 24 4STR 4AGI 6CHA 6INT<br><br>Ronney &lt;Nexus of Dreams&gt;<br>Antonius Bayle<br><br><br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Wed Jan  8 21:11:40 2003</em></p>&nbsp;<br> </td></td></tr>
