	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=135979><span id=Scholar>RavinRed</span></a><br><b><span id=Scholar>Scholar</span></b><br><span id=notbold>75 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good [3.50]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>IT's not necessarily any easier to get, but you ought to take a look at Heradlic Armor.&nbsp;&nbsp;It's player-made, tends to run spendy (I'm subsidising a blacksmith right now to eventually get mine at cost).  Most is deity-specific, but Fine Heraldic seems to be good general-purpose Human armor.<br><br><a href=HTTP://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/fast_search.html?classes=0&amp;race=0&amp;type=Any+Slot&amp;stat=None&amp;pristat=ac&amp;priwt=2&amp;secstat=hp&amp;secwt=1&amp;tristat=none&amp;triwt=0&amp;level=&amp;price=&amp;qt=b&amp;st=Heraldic target=_new>All Heraldic Armor</a><br><br>Calthine Faeriesong<br>Faithful Battle Bard of Torture<br>Vazelle</p>&nbsp;<br><a href=HTTP://calthine.tripod.com target=_new>Calthine Faeriesong</a><br>53 Minstrel <br>Vazelle</td></td></tr>
